{"tid":959762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那跪低】被指非法工作被拘留   支那不敵壓力釋放加拿大女教師麥克弗回國","createTime":"2018-12-29T00:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T00:48:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf869002478ae461ff9693c54771fc1474c7ee8b","tid":959762,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T00:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181229/large/1546039654_6b0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181229%2Flarge%2F1546039654_6b0b.jpg&h=0abb797c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181229/59082117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59082117&d=0c4mArMl0E%2BZfWPrXi2OEjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0f96cc38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59082117&h=a4fc265c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181229/59082117</a><br />\n因被指非法工作問題而被支那地方公安機關扣留的加拿大教師，已獲釋放。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大全球事務部發言人沃克(Richard Walker)說，本月較早時被支那拘留的教師麥克弗（Sarah McIver），已獲釋返家。<br />\n<br />\n麥克弗是支那政府扣留的第三名加拿大公民，在她之前，前外交官康明凱(Michael Kovrig)和商人斯帕沃(Michael Spavor)，先後因涉嫌因損害支那國家安全而被中國拘留。外間一般認為支那此舉，是要報復加拿大應美國要求，扣留電訊商華為副董事長孟晚舟。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"ffd197625807cf133eea0c05d617bf47b205ff8f","tid":959762,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"喳架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406e6436e845a36883b293d363e65ebaa163cb57","tid":959762,"uid":61280,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x